name: Moses
message:
Howdy! I understand this is sort of off-topic however I needed to ask.
Does managing a well-established website like yours require 
a large amount of work? I'm brand new to writing a blog however I do write in my journal everyday.
I'd like to start a blog so I can easily share my personal experience and views online.
Please let me know if you have any recommendations 
or tips for brand new aspiring blog owners.
Appreciate it!
